Taste wise these babies get 5 stars.  But it contains sugar alcohols, and the side effects for some of us are simply not worth the sweet treat.  Until some genius figures out how to use stevia instead of the evil hell creature that is maltitol, I will not touch these things ever again.  If you love em, have some pepto or activated charcoal next to you and prepare to isolate yourself in a well ventilated room for a day.  You have been warned.
